= Development Meeting - Virtual - 2026 Meeting #1 =

== Dates ==

Jun 16th 2026 [https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/meetingtime.html?iso=20260616&p1=43&p2=256&p3=215&p4=371 (4 PM - 5 PM UTC)]


== Goals ==

The main aim is to plan release of PostGIS 3.7.0
 * GEOS Release of 3.15.0
 * PostGIS core and raster, assume we are done with adding functions
 * PostGIS SFCGAL - any additional functions to add
 * PostGIS Topology - any outstanding functions to add
 * PostGIS 3.7.0 Plans
 * Packager unforseen issues with moving address_standardizer
   and postgis_tiger_geocoder to separate repos
 * Packager any unforseen issues now the h3-pg is under PostGIS org
 * Security patches and release
    * More bug reports about security, many uncovered by AI - mostly impact cloud providers
    * Release cycles more frequent as a result
    * How do we get funding for this?
 * PostGIS budget of $2000 from [https://wiki.osgeo.org/wiki/OSGeo_Budget_2026#OSGeo_Projects OSGeo], and $2000 for GEOS, plans for spending
 * LLM Policy
 * AI skills files, how should they be structured?

